<cas :data="options" @on-change="handleChange" :loadData="loadOption" transfer>
  <v-combobox multiple :label="label" chips clearable v-model="selected" :required="required"
    :rules="defaultRules">
    <template v-slot:selection="{ item, parent, selected }">
      <v-chip @click.stop="" v-if="multiple" close @input="remove(item)" small outline color="green">
        {{ item.label}} 
      </v-chip>
      <v-chip @click.stop="" v-else small>{{ item}}</v-chip>
    </template>
  </v-combobox>
</cas>
